---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<Layout title="Awards">
  <Header />

  <main class="py-8">
    <HeroSection 
      title="Awards"
      description="See how our customers are achieving success with Green Orbit Digital"
    />

    <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-secondary-500">

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
    
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Awards & Recognition</h1>

    <div class="space-y-10">

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">An Award-Winning Agency Driving Sustainable Impact in Space Marketing</h2>
        <p>
          At Green Orbit Digital, we take pride in our commitment to excellence, innovation, and measurable impact.
          Our work has been recognised across the space industry and sustainability sectors, reflecting the rigour, creativity, 
          and partnership-driven approach we bring to every client engagement.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Global Recognition for Innovation and Sustainability</h2>
        <p>
          From pioneering sustainable marketing strategies to advancing the narrative around environmental responsibility in space,
          Green Orbit Digital has earned accolades that underscore our leadership and expertise.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2">
          Our awards and commendations span international sustainability forums, space innovation conferences, and 
          digital marketing excellence awards — affirming our role as trusted partners to clients who want to create 
          lasting, positive change.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Championing Your Growth and Sustainable Success</h2>
        <p>
          We don’t just celebrate our achievements — we channel that momentum into supporting your organisation’s sustainable growth.
          Whether through bespoke marketing strategies, data-driven impact measurement, or strategic communications, 
          we help you unlock new opportunities and build credibility in a rapidly evolving space economy.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Examples of Our Awards and Commendations</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
          <li>Recognition for pioneering sustainable marketing frameworks in the space sector</li>
          <li>Awards for innovative digital campaigns that reduce carbon footprint and drive engagement</li>
          <li>Commendations for thought leadership on sustainable space industry practices</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Join Our Journey of Excellence</h2>
        <p>
          With a track record of award-winning projects and a deep commitment to sustainability, 
          Green Orbit Digital is your trusted partner in navigating the complexities of space sector marketing.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2">
          <strong>Get in touch</strong> to discover how we can help your organisation achieve its next big win in sustainable growth and impact.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Explore More</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
          <li><a href="/capabilities" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Our Capabilities</a></li>
          <li><a href="/sustainability" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Sustainability Approach</a></li>
          <li><a href="/partnerships" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Partnerships</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Contact Us</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>